{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"lrc":{"version":18,"lyric":"[00:11.133]I saw the wild flowers dying as we froze in the winter\n[00:17.568]Lost my clothes in the water, feel the sand between my toes\n[00:23.178]All these days we kept trying put our hands on the lions\n[00:29.378]Never thoughtwe'd stop flying, just to walk this on our own\n[00:35.175]Ohwe're growing old now\n[00:40.636]Will it ever be the same\n[00:46.142]Since we slowed down\n[00:49.780]We slowed down\n[00:52.679]We slowed down\n[00:55.737]We slowed down slowed down\n[00:58.523]Slowed down slowed down\n[01:01.274]We slowed down slowed down\n[01:04.096]Slowed down down, down\n[01:08.620]We slowed down\n[01:32.578]We slowed down\n[01:34.944]We slowed down\n[01:36.387]We slowed down\n[01:37.792]We slowed down\n[01:39.205]We slowed down\n[01:40.722]We slowed down\n[01:42.242]We slowed, slowed down\n[01:46.747]We slowed down\n[01:48.172]We slowed down\n[01:49.518]We slowed down\n[01:50.969]We slowed down\n[01:52.397]We slowed down\n[01:53.914]We slowed, slowed down\n[01:58.849]And nowwe're too deep in the water, Ican't see you anymore see you anymore...\n[02:10.115]We slowed down,it's too late to recover\n[02:16.670]I justcan't see you anymore\n[02:25.335]Ican't do this anymore, more\n[02:30.981]You can knock but I shut the door, door\n[02:37.095]Idon't want this to be a chore\n[02:45.778]We slowed down\n[02:48.881]We slowed down\n[02:51.803]We slowed down\n[02:54.791]We slowed down\n[03:00.464]Down, down, down, down\n[03:06.406]We slowed down\n[03:30.097]We slowed down\n[03:32.315]We slowed down\n[03:33.870]We slowed down\n[03:35.356]We slowed down\n[03:36.791]We slowed down\n[03:38.339]We slowed down\n[03:39.748]We slowed, slowed down\n[03:44.106]We slowed down\n[03:45.546]We slowed down\n[03:47.032]We slowed down\n[03:48.425]We slowed down\n[03:49.903]We slowed down\n[03:51.401]We slowed, slowed down\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":2,"lyric":"[00:11.133]冰原千里 而花海却被凛冬吞没\n[00:17.568]在这刺骨的寒泉中我一丝不挂 任沙把我的双脚覆没\n[00:23.178]日子越是走过 我们就越狂妄\n[00:29.378]从未想过停止飞翔 用脚走路\n[00:35.175]但我们终将老去\n[00:40.636]还会和曾经一样吗\n[00:46.142]所以我们渐渐放缓了\n[00:49.780]放缓了\n[00:52.679]疲惫了\n[00:55.737]不再狂妄了\n[00:58.523]放缓了\n[01:01.274]放缓了\n[01:04.096]放缓了\n[01:08.620]想要停下\n[01:32.578]想要停下\n[01:34.944]放缓了\n[01:36.387]放缓了\n[01:37.792]慢下来吧\n[01:39.205]我们放缓了\n[01:40.722]放慢步子\n[01:42.242]放慢生活\n[01:46.747]放慢孤独\n[01:48.172]放慢思索\n[01:49.518]放缓了\n[01:50.969]终于放缓了\n[01:52.397]时间变慢\n[01:53.914]我们才会停下 停下\n[01:58.849]如今我们沉入冰河 你的轮廓逐渐模糊\n[02:10.115]我们慢了下来 却再无法相见\n[02:16.670]我恐怕再无法与你相见\n[02:25.335]放弃吧\n[02:30.981]任你寻觅 我总不肯相见\n[02:37.095]我不想再让世间乏味之事打扰我\n[02:45.778]所以我放缓了\n[02:48.881]亦疲惫了\n[02:51.803]放慢了\n[02:54.791]任时间飞逝\n[03:00.464]孤单 虚弱 无力 沉沦\n[03:06.406]放缓了\n[03:30.097]放缓了\n[03:32.315]放缓了\n[03:33.870]亦失望\n[03:35.356]亦彷徨\n[03:36.791]放慢步子\n[03:38.339]放慢时间\n[03:39.748]放空生活\n[03:44.106]放慢旅程\n[03:45.546]冰冷渐至\n[03:47.032]万物冷然\n[03:48.425]我渐放慢\n[03:49.903]我渐放慢\n[03:51.401]我曾孤单\n"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"code":200}